WORKFLOW — CONTENT EDIT

When editing a stay:
1. Check if content is source or GED edited
2. Modify only GED fields
3. Protect from sync overwrite
4. Verify front display

WORKFLOW — BUG FIX

1. Identify bug location
2. Minimal fix only
3. Verify no route broken
4. Confirm UI + data OK

WORKFLOW — DEPLOY

Before deploy:
1. Build must succeed
2. No missing images
3. No console errors
4. Main pages tested
